channel.title: What else can I take out?
channel.description:
What else can I take out of client.java to make it smaller. In our current project we are making it like RuneScape, andcurrently it's at 920.1kb, before we took out all the methods, voids, and commands it was at .99MB
Right now instead, we are going to make them spawn with books in there inventory, and it explains how to earn money ect ect, but the question is, what else can we take out.
